OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FIsrael has struck southern suburbs in
OL,7,FBeirut without warning, defying a US
OL,8,Frequest not to attack the capital amid
OL,9,Fthe ongoing ceasefire agreement.
OL,11,FTwo people were killed and 11 others
OL,12,Finjured in the strikes, which hit a
OL,13,Fresidential building and damaged four
OL,14,Ffloors, Lebanon's state-run national
OL,15,Fnews agency said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
