OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FA statement from Israeli Prime
OL,7,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu's office
OL,8,Fsaid the strikes were in retaliation
OL,9,Ffor Hezbollah firing toward northern
OL,10,FIsrael, and that the attacks targeted
OL,11,F"command centres" in the neighborhoods.
OL,13,F"We are striking them very hard, and
OL,14,Fwe know that Hezbollah is on the run,"
OL,15,FNetanyahu told his cabinet.
