OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FHezbollah has not immediately claimed
OL,7,Fresponsibility for firing at Israel.
OL,9,FThe strike comes days after a
OL,10,Fceasefire agreed between Israel and
OL,11,FLebanon in Washington went into effect.
OL,13,FIran had warned that an attack on
OL,14,FBeirut would renew full-scale war
OL,15,Facross the Middle East, despite
OL,16,FPakistan's attempts to manage talks
OL,17,Fbetween Tehran and Washington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
