OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FThe nation wants a deal to include
OL,7,Fending the war in Lebanon, but
OL,8,Fnegotiations have come to a stalemate
OL,9,Fas the war hit 100 days on Sunday.
OL,11,FIranian MP Ebrahim Rezaei, who is a
OL,12,Fspokesperson for Iran's national
OL,13,Fsecurity, wrote on X that Tehran
OL,14,Fwould give a "painful" response to
OL,15,FIsrael's attack on Beirut.
OL,17,FHe warned the nation: "Look at the sky
OL,18,Fover the occupied lands tonight."
OL,20,FTrump says Iran deal "very close"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
