OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump told NBC's
OL,7,F"Meet the Press" in an interview aired
OL,8,FSunday he is not demanding Lebanon be
OL,9,Fpart of the deal with Iran, but said
OL,10,Fhe'd like to see the country have a
OL,11,F"better life".
OL,13,F"I'd like to see Lebanon have a better
OL,14,Flife. I'd like to see a more surgical
OL,15,Fattack on Hezbollah. I think it should
OL,16,Fbe more surgical," Trump said.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
