OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FThe president also repeated his claims
OL,7,Fthat the US and Iran are "very close"
OL,8,Fto finalising the deal to end the war,
OL,9,Fstating that he was finding the
OL,10,Fregime's new leadership "more
OL,11,Frational, very smart".
OL,13,FTrump said he had not spoken directly
OL,14,Fwith Supreme Leader Mojtaba Khamenei,
OL,15,Fwho has not been seen in public since
OL,16,Fthe war began, and speculated that he
OL,17,Fwas "pretty badly injured".
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@UO]
