OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FThe president also said the US would
OL,7,Fwork with Iran to retrieve and destroy
OL,8,Fthe nation's highly enriched uranium
OL,9,Fif a deal is struck, but warned the
OL,10,Fmaterial will be collected by force if
OL,11,Fno agreement is made.
OL,13,F"If we make a deal that now we're
OL,14,Ffriendly, we'll all go together. It'll
OL,15,Fbe our equipment. We'll take it out
OL,16,Fand destroy it, whether it's on-site
OL,17,For whether we take it off-site," Trump
OL,18,Fsaid.
