OL,6,F"Now, if we don't make a deal, then
OL,7,Fwe're going to take them out
OL,8,Fmilitarily very harshly. And we'll
OL,9,Fwait till we do that before we go, in
OL,10,Fwhich case we'll have safety either
OL,11,Fway."
OL,13,FUS Central Command said that US forces
OL,14,Fhad shot down two Iranian one-way
OL,15,Fattack drones that threatened
OL,16,Finternational maritime traffic in the
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz during the early
OL,18,Fhours of Sunday morning.
