OL,6,F"American forces remain postured and
OL,7,Fready to continue defending against
OL,8,FIranian aggression," it said in a post
OL,9,Fon X.
OL,11,FStrikes on Gaza kill four as one dead
OL,12,Fin Israel shooting
OL,14,FAt least four Palestinians were killed
OL,15,Fin an Israeli airstrike that hit a
OL,16,Fpolice point in Gaza's southern city
OL,17,Fof Khan Younis, according to the
OL,18,FPalestinian Red Crescent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
