OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FThe dead were taken to a field
OL,7,Fhospital run by the Red Crescent, and
OL,8,Fat least 10 others were wounded, the
OL,9,Fcharity said.
OL,11,FIn Israel, a Palestinian gunman with
OL,12,FIsraeli citizenship killed one person
OL,13,Fand wounded five others in a rampage
OL,14,Fthrough multiple towns close to the
OL,15,Fboundary with the occupied West Bank.
OL,17,FFears of a widespread attack prompted
OL,18,Fauthorities to order residents to stay
OL,19,Fat home, and children at school in the
OL,20,Farea were kept in lockdown for at
OL,21,Fleast three hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
