OL,3,CIsrael strikes Beirut days after US-
OL,4,Csupported ceasefire deal
OL,6,FTensions have been heightened amid a
OL,7,Fspate of Israeli settler attacks, and
OL,8,Fthe death of a Palestinian baby over
OL,9,Fthe weekend, who was killed when
OL,10,FIsraeli troops fired at a car.
OL,12,FSeven-month-old Sam Fahd Abu Haikal
OL,13,Fwas killed Friday evening, and his
OL,14,Fparents were wounded while driving in
OL,15,Fthe Tel Rumeida area south of Hebron
OL,16,FCity, according to the Palestinian
OL,17,Fhealth ministry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
